{"tid":452321,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拍拖拍到好無力","createTime":"2017-10-30T05:34:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T07:12:07.000Z","uid":85219,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b4e17cbc52c7ae0f6717cbbe5c7bc981815ea58d","tid":452321,"uid":85219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T05:34:31.000Z","msg":"男朋友日日都要練波<br />\n平時返學又返到好夜<br />\n星期日又要陪屋企人<br />\n身為一個好女朋友應該要支持佢打波，去打大賽<br />\n但係我都想好似平常人咁出下街一齊打下機<br />\n而唔係得送佢打波，接佢打波<br />\n我都知佢有多餘嘅時間都用黎陪我，都係其實都係得上堂見到嘅時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以開解下我，我係咪好唔知足"},{"pid":"f91882dd8d5d0eab2162819466b74e438135650a","tid":452321,"uid":20448,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T05:41:25.000Z","msg":"佢值得搵個更好既女朋友"},{"pid":"4174063247c6c470100b2808ef5327c192014f2d","tid":452321,"uid":76105,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T05:41:46.000Z","msg":"佢碌鳩痕咪會諗起你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你只係一個飛機杯"},{"pid":"8c65e7f313e2205856d9cb95c39beb3c23846458","tid":452321,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T05:43:32.000Z","msg":"扑嘢有無力"},{"pid":"1eb05c7267719d22a8be9e4f0dd24523e3748f1c","tid":452321,"uid":139225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T05:48:38.000Z","msg":"你嘅生活得佢<br />\n佢嘅生活多姿多彩<br />\n搵野做下啦"},{"pid":"9b488556c3db2d1656979d3c955a5671beb4f530","tid":452321,"uid":53090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:02:32.000Z","msg":"死啦～睇錯拍航拍拍都冇力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf09547d587e83994b03544c972ce17218b50a4","tid":452321,"uid":85219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:07:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢碌鳩痕咪會諗起你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你只係一個飛機杯</blockquote><br />\n佢真係專一㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係佢玩運動無時間<br />\n咁我無可能叫佢放棄自己興趣陪我㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"395eaac026fbff870cdd4d5453eba2f0b43d131c","tid":452321,"uid":85219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:09:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你嘅生活得佢<br />\n佢嘅生活多姿多彩<br />\n搵野做下啦</blockquote><br />\n我都覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以依家都有去做gym 想身型再好啲襯起佢多啲<br />\n平時睇佢打比賽練波都激起我做運動嘅決心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a90a6210eb67bcd66ef9ae6ae14bf4dcc3be4d","tid":452321,"uid":44854,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:09:58.000Z","msg":"女人就係唔識細水長流，唔會珍惜<br />\n佢有佢既野做，你唔鐘意咪做下其他野，得閒先去支持佢囉"},{"pid":"27857fdb3094741e5f0a639eef4f54ee6fb85631","tid":452321,"uid":85219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:11:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扑嘢有無力</blockquote><br />\n有啊<br />\n只係有時心痛佢打波已經好攰<br />\n拍左年幾 一星期一次到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2681a1a0ed73dfddd4f614b648d35fc39989302","tid":452321,"uid":85219,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:13:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女人就係唔識細水長流，唔會珍惜<br />\n佢有佢既野做，你唔鐘意咪做下其他野，得閒先去支持佢囉</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得佢唔夠珍惜我多啲喎<br />\n我無唔比佢做佢想做嘅野 又無因為佢打波發脾氣<br />\n只係自己有啲唔開心"},{"pid":"f5a97de3abd4ded3e7d5d71cce10bbe2e78f22a1","tid":452321,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:26:27.000Z","msg":"分囉，最撚煩就係你呢d女"},{"pid":"7b3a5ad4be09c20d2c712b39b4a48d4b55601cf6","tid":452321,"uid":93202,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T07:08:20.000Z","msg":"咪聽啲ON9毒撚UP啦樓主<br />\n既然你冇發過老脾嘅, 我諗你EQ都唔錯<br />\n直接同佢講下你有被忽略嘅感覺, 係女仔都想要人陪下<br />\n如果佢話真係好想全心全意去打左個比賽先<br />\n咪約定打完之後比D時間黎陪你, 一齊去玩下去旅行之類囉<br />\n最緊要係溝通<br />\n你收埋收埋自己唔開心, 段關係好易有怨氣<br />\n到最後都係搞着自己"},{"pid":"0dd8ce0577c94